{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"密碼套件","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Cipher_suite","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>密碼套件是包括了密鑰交換算法，身份認證方法，批量加密密碼(<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cipher\">cipher <small>(en-US)</small></a>)和消息認證碼的組合.</p>\n<p>在密碼系統(<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\">cryptosystem</a>)裏像 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/TLS\">TLS <small>(en-US)</small></a>, 客戶端和伺服器在它們開始安全的通訊之前必須同意密碼套件。典型的密碼套件如 ECDHE_RSA_WITH_AES_128_GCM_SHA256 或 ECDHE-RSA-AES128-GCM-SHA256, 具有如下特徵:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>ECDHE (橢圓曲綫數字簽名算法) 進行密鑰交換</li>\n  <li>RSA 進行認證</li>\n  <li>AES-128 作爲密碼和伽羅瓦/計數器模式 (GCM) 作爲分組密碼模式的操作</li>\n  <li>SHA-256 作爲基於散列的消息認證碼(HMAC)</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://wiki.mozilla.org/Security/Server_Side_TLS\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Mozilla 推薦 TLS 的密碼套件選擇</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"密碼套件是包括了密鑰交換算法，身份認證方法，批量加密密碼(cipher (en-US))和消息認證碼的組合.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Cipher suite","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Suite de chiffrement","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Cipher suite (暗号スイート)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"密码套件","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/cipher_suite","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/cipher_suite/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Cipher_suite","title":"密碼套件"}],"pageTitle":"密碼套件 - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}